title: [Milkin' It]
description: Wispy clouds of chiffon-wrapped glass are interspersed across the vibrant blue-painted ceiling, the semi-translucent lanterns encircling a gilded glass sphere at the center of the shop.  A red barn-shaped display sits nestled across rugs of grass-colored cotton, the neatly stacked wares cushioned in a bright gingham cloth.  Diminutive figurines of roltons, goats, and other farm animals are displayed on several wall-mounted shelves, the models crafted from a variety of artistic mediums.
